div.h1: EOI Flow: Master vs Slave PIC

ul.li:
IRQ0-7: Send EOI to Master PIC only
outb(0x20, 0x20)

IRQ8-15: Send EOI to BOTH PICs
First: outb(0xA0, 0x20) (Slave)
Then: outb(0x20, 0x20) (Master) Why both for IRQ8-15? Slave PIC signals master via IRQ2. Both have interrupt "in progress" state. Both require acknowledgment.
